Program: Omnibus
Title: Lotta and the Englishmen
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p0376l8n
Last Broadcast Date: 15 July 1996
Young Swedish writer Lotta Erikson comes to England to find the perfect man. Each day she meets up with a different stranger in a cafe. She has been fantasising for years about England and Englishmen, but what will she make of the real thing?